cs.IR, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV 

This paper deals with the visualization of semantics in text data, specifically in the domain of filmscript analysis. It incorporates techniques such as tag clouds, reduced dimensionality mapping, and Kohonen self-organizing maps. These techniques are commonly used in the fields of information retrieval (cs.IR), natural language processing (cs.CL), machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
